OL,4,CA-level results: Students have been
OL,5,Ctreated fairly - watchdog
OL,6, Students getting results this week can
OL,7, feel satisfied that their grades are
OL,8, fair, the head of the exams watchdog
OL,9, has said.
OL,11,FSimon Lebus from Ofqual - which
OL,12,Foversees exams in England - strongly
OL,13,Fdefended the system for deciding
OL,14,FA-level and GCSE results this year.
OL,16,FHe said teacher assessments give a
OL,17,F"much more accurate reflection" of what
OL,18,Fstudents can achieve.
OL,20,FBut he said while pupils can appeal a
OL,21,Fteacher's judgement, the bar is high.
